      { text: `Verifying coordinates [${latVal.toFixed(4)}, ${lngVal.toFixed(4)}]...`, v: "Media Loaded.", g: `Locked [${latVal.toFixed(4)}, ${lngVal.toFixed(4)}]`, s: "Scanning Hazards..." },
      { text: "Analyzing severity hazard index...", v: "Media Verified.", g: `Locked [${latVal.toFixed(4)}, ${lngVal.toFixed(4)}]`, s: "Determining SLA Class..." },
      { text: "Finalizing civic report...", v: "Complete.", g: "Complete.", s: "Complete." }
    ];

    let currentStep = 0;
    
    const interval = setInterval(() => {
      currentStep++;
      if (currentStep < states.length) {
        if (aiStatusText) aiStatusText.textContent = states[currentStep].text;
        if (aiVision) aiVision.textContent = states[currentStep].v;
        if (aiGeo) aiGeo.textContent = states[currentStep].g;
        if (aiSeverity) aiSeverity.textContent = states[currentStep].s;
      } else {
        clearInterval(interval);
        finalizeAIReport();
      }
    }, 700);

    function finalizeAIReport() {
      aiOverlay?.classList.add('hidden');
      aiOverlay?.classList.remove('flex');

      let imageUrl = "/images/pothole_vadodara.png";
      if (uploadedImageUrl) {
        imageUrl = uploadedImageUrl;
      } else {
        if (mediaSelection === 'streetlight') imageUrl = "/images/streetlight_vadodara.png";
        if (mediaSelection === 'water') imageUrl = "/images/water_vadodara.png";
        if (mediaSelection === 'garbage') imageUrl = "/images/garbage_vadodara.png";
      }

      const newIssue = {
        id: "issue-" + Date.now(),
        title,
        description,
        category,
        severity,
        status: "Open",
        locality,
        verifications: 0,
        lat: latVal,
        lng: lngVal,
        date: new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0],
        reportedBy: (() => {
          const isLoggedIn = localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_is_logged_in') === 'true';
          const loggedInUser = localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_logged_in_user');
          if (isLoggedIn && loggedInUser) {
            try {
              return JSON.parse(loggedInUser).name + " (You)";
            } catch (e) {}
          }
          return "Ritvik Vedangi (You)";
        })(),
        imageUrl
      };

      const issues = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_issues') || '[]');
      issues.unshift(newIssue);
      localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_issues', JSON.stringify(issues));

      const userStats = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_user_stats') || '{"points": 350, "level": "Civic Scout"}');
      userStats.points += 100;
      localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_user_stats', JSON.stringify(userStats));

      showToast(`AI analysis complete. Category: ${category} (${severity} Severity). Plotted on map! +100 Civic points!`);

      renderFeed();
      updateStatsWidgets();
      
      window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('pinpoint_issues_updated'));
    }
  });

  window.addEventListener('pinpoint_select_issue', (e: any) => {
    const id = e.detail.id;
    const card = document.getElementById(`feed-card-${id}`);
    
    if (card) {
      const allCards = document.querySelectorAll('[id^="feed-card-"]');
      allCards.forEach(c => c.classList.remove('border-primary', 'bg-primary/5'));

      card.classList.add('border-primary', 'bg-primary/5');
      card.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'nearest' });
    }
  });

  window.addEventListener('pinpoint_clear_highlights', () => {
    const allCards = document.querySelectorAll('[id^="feed-card-"]');
    allCards.forEach(c => c.classList.remove('border-primary', 'bg-primary/5'));
  });

  searchInput?.addEventListener('input', renderFeed);
  categoryFilter?.addEventListener('change', renderFeed);
  statusFilter?.addEventListener('change', renderFeed);

  // Auth & Profile Modal DOM bindings
  const authModal = document.getElementById('auth-modal');
  const authForm = document.getElementById('auth-form') as HTMLFormElement;
  const authCloseBtn = document.getElementById('auth-modal-close-btn');
  const profileModal = document.getElementById('profile-modal');
  const profileCloseBtn = document.getElementById('profile-modal-close-btn');
  const logoutBtn = document.getElementById('profile-logout-btn');
  
  const tabLogin = document.getElementById('tab-login');
  const tabSignup = document.getElementById('tab-signup');
  const fieldName = document.getElementById('auth-field-name');
  const authTitle = document.getElementById('auth-modal-title');
  const authSubmitBtn = document.getElementById('auth-submit-btn');

  let authMode: 'login' | 'signup' = 'login';
  
  tabLogin?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    authMode = 'login';
    tabLogin.className = "flex-1 text-center py-1.5 rounded-md text-xs font-bold bg-canvas text-ink shadow-sm transition-all cursor-pointer";
    tabSignup!.className = "flex-1 text-center py-1.5 rounded-md text-xs font-semibold text-muted hover:text-ink transition-all cursor-pointer";
    fieldName?.classList.add('hidden');
    (document.getElementById('auth-name') as HTMLInputElement).required = false;
    if (authTitle) authTitle.textContent = "Sign In";
    if (authSubmitBtn) authSubmitBtn.textContent = "Log In";
  });
  
  tabSignup?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    authMode = 'signup';
    tabSignup.className = "flex-1 text-center py-1.5 rounded-md text-xs font-bold bg-canvas text-ink shadow-sm transition-all cursor-pointer";
    tabLogin.className = "flex-1 text-center py-1.5 rounded-md text-xs font-semibold text-muted hover:text-ink transition-all cursor-pointer";
    fieldName?.classList.remove('hidden');
    (document.getElementById('auth-name') as HTMLInputElement).required = true;
    if (authTitle) authTitle.textContent = "Create Account";
    if (authSubmitBtn) authSubmitBtn.textContent = "Create Account";
  });

  function openAuthModal() {
    authModal?.classList.remove('hidden');
    syncScrollLock();
  }
  
  function closeAuthModal() {
    authModal?.classList.add('hidden');
    syncScrollLock();
    authForm.reset();
  }
  
  function openProfileModal() {
    profileModal?.classList.remove('hidden');
    syncScrollLock();
    
    // Set profile details dynamically
    const userStats = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_user_stats') || '{"points": 350, "level": "Civic Scout"}');
    const loggedInUser = localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_logged_in_user');
    let name = "Ritvik Vedangi";
    let initials = "RV";
    
    if (loggedInUser) {
      try {
        const u = JSON.parse(loggedInUser);
        name = u.name;
        initials = u.name.split(' ').map((n: string) => n[0]).join('').toUpperCase().substring(0, 2);
      } catch (e) {
        console.error(e);
      }
    }
    
    const profModalName = document.getElementById('profile-modal-name');
    const profModalBadge = document.getElementById('profile-modal-badge');
    const profModalPoints = document.getElementById('profile-modal-points');
    const profModalAvatar = document.getElementById('profile-modal-avatar');
    
    if (profModalName) profModalName.textContent = name;
    if (profModalBadge) profModalBadge.textContent = userStats.level;
    if (profModalPoints) profModalPoints.textContent = userStats.points;
    if (profModalAvatar) profModalAvatar.textContent = initials;
  }
  
  function closeProfileModal() {
    profileModal?.classList.add('hidden');
    syncScrollLock();
  }
  
  authCloseBtn?.addEventListener('click', closeAuthModal);
  authModal?.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    if (e.target === authModal) closeAuthModal();
  });
  
  profileCloseBtn?.addEventListener('click', closeProfileModal);
  profileModal?.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    if (e.target === profileModal) closeProfileModal();
  });
  
  // Register custom events for navbar mapping
  window.addEventListener('pinpoint_open_auth_modal', openAuthModal);
  window.addEventListener('pinpoint_open_profile_modal', openProfileModal);

  // Auth Form submit logic
  authForm?.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    
    const email = (document.getElementById('auth-email') as HTMLInputElement).value;
    const password = (document.getElementById('auth-password') as HTMLInputElement).value;
    
    let users = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_users') || '[]');
    
    if (authMode === 'signup') {
      const name = (document.getElementById('auth-name') as HTMLInputElement).value;
      
      // Check if user already exists
      if (users.some((u: any) => u.email === email)) {
        showToast("An account with this email already exists!");
        return;
      }
      
      const newUser = {
        name,
        email,
        password,
        points: 350,
        level: "Civic Scout"
      };
      
      users.push(newUser);
      localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_users', JSON.stringify(users));
      
      // Log in the new user
      localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_is_logged_in', 'true');
      localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_logged_in_user', JSON.stringify(newUser));
      localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_user_stats', JSON.stringify({ points: 350, level: "Civic Scout" }));
      
      // Add or update entry in leaderboard
      let leaderboard = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_leaderboard') || '[]');
      const userIndex = leaderboard.findIndex((l: any) => l.isUser === true);
      if (userIndex !== -1) {
        leaderboard[userIndex].name = `You (${name})`;
        leaderboard[userIndex].points = 350;
        leaderboard[userIndex].badge = "Civic Scout";
      } else {
        leaderboard.push({ name: `You (${name})`, points: 350, issues: 3, badge: "Civic Scout", isUser: true });
      }
      localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_leaderboard', JSON.stringify(leaderboard));
      
      showToast(`Welcome ${name}! Account created and signed in.`);
    } else {
      // Login mode
      const user = users.find((u: any) => u.email === email && u.password === password);
      
      // Fallback for default seed user (Ritvik Vedangi)
      const defaultUser = { name: "Ritvik Vedangi", email: "ritvik@example.com", password: "password123", points: 350, level: "Civic Scout" };
      
      if (email === "ritvik@example.com" && password === "password123") {
        localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_is_logged_in', 'true');
        localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_logged_in_user', JSON.stringify(defaultUser));
        localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_user_stats', JSON.stringify({ points: defaultUser.points, level: defaultUser.level }));
        
        let leaderboard = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_leaderboard') || '[]');
        const userIndex = leaderboard.findIndex((l: any) => l.isUser === true);
        if (userIndex !== -1) {
          leaderboard[userIndex].name = `You (${defaultUser.name})`;
        }
        localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_leaderboard', JSON.stringify(leaderboard));
        
        showToast("Signed in successfully as Ritvik Vedangi!");
      } else if (user) {
        localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_is_logged_in', 'true');
        localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_logged_in_user', JSON.stringify(user));
        localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_user_stats', JSON.stringify({ points: user.points, level: user.level }));
        
        let leaderboard = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_leaderboard') || '[]');
        const userIndex = leaderboard.findIndex((l: any) => l.isUser === true);
        if (userIndex !== -1) {
          leaderboard[userIndex].name = `You (${user.name})`;
          leaderboard[userIndex].points = user.points;
          leaderboard[userIndex].badge = user.level;
        }
        localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_leaderboard', JSON.stringify(leaderboard));
        
        showToast(`Signed in successfully as ${user.name}!`);
      } else {
        showToast("Invalid email or password!");
        return;
      }
    }
    
    closeAuthModal();
    
    // Dispatch events to refresh navbar and components
    window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('pinpoint_auth_changed'));
    renderLeaderboard();
    updateStatsWidgets();
  });

  // Logout logic
  logoutBtn?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    // Save current points back to the user database in localStorage before logging out
    const isLoggedIn = localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_is_logged_in') === 'true';
    const loggedInUser = localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_logged_in_user');
    if (isLoggedIn && loggedInUser) {
      try {
        const u = JSON.parse(loggedInUser);
        const userStats = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_user_stats') || '{"points": 350, "level": "Civic Scout"}');
        let users = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_users') || '[]');
        const userIndex = users.findIndex((usr: any) => usr.email === u.email);
        if (userIndex !== -1) {
          users[userIndex].points = userStats.points;
          users[userIndex].level = userStats.level;
          localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_users', JSON.stringify(users));
        }
      } catch (e) {
        console.error(e);
      }
    }

    localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_is_logged_in', 'false');
    localStorage.removeItem('pinpoint_logged_in_user');
    // Set guest user stats
    localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_user_stats', JSON.stringify({ points: 350, level: "Civic Scout" }));
    
    let leaderboard = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('pinpoint_leaderboard') || '[]');
    const userIndex = leaderboard.findIndex((l: any) => l.isUser === true);
    if (userIndex !== -1) {
      leaderboard[userIndex].name = "You (Guest Citizen)";
      leaderboard[userIndex].points = 350;
      leaderboard[userIndex].badge = "Civic Scout";
    }
    localStorage.setItem('pinpoint_leaderboard', JSON.stringify(leaderboard));
    
    showToast("Signed out successfully.");
    closeProfileModal();
    
    // Dispatch events to refresh navbar and components
    window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('pinpoint_auth_changed'));
    renderLeaderboard();
    updateStatsWidgets();
  });

  renderFeed();
  updateStatsWidgets();
  });
</script>

<style>
  /* Local animations */
  @keyframes spin {
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }
  @keyframes reverse-spin {
    to { transform: rotate(-360deg); }
  }
  .animate-spin {
    animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
  }
  .animate-reverse-spin {
    animation: reverse-spin 1.5s linear infinite;
  }
  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1) forwards;
  }
  .animate-scale-up {
    animation: scaleUp 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1) forwards;
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes scaleUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.9); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
  }
  .animate-toast-slide-up {
    animation: toastSlideUpFade 3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1) forwards;
  }
  @keyframes toastSlideUpFade {
    0% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(-50%, 20px); }
    10% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, 0); }
    90% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, 0); }
    100% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(-50%, -20px); }
  }
</style>
